00:34:54,502 --> 00:34:57,172
I actually do more
of the creative work,

00:34:57,172 --> 00:34:59,407
um, but we collaborate
on the design.

00:34:59,407 --> 00:35:01,042
We kind of pass things
back and forth

00:35:01,042 --> 00:35:03,912
